  • java.lang.Object

  • Type Parameters:
    TSource - Element type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<TSource>, Enumerable<TSource>, ExtendedEnumerable<TSource>, ExtendedOrderedEnumerable<TSource>, ExtendedOrderedQueryable<TSource>, ExtendedQueryable<TSource>, OrderedEnumerable<TSource>, OrderedQueryable<TSource>, Queryable<TSource>, RawEnumerable<TSource>, RawQueryable<TSource>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CalciteConnectionImpl.CalciteQueryable, QueryProviderImpl.QueryableImpl
    public abstract class BaseQueryable<TSource>
extends AbstractQueryable<TSource>
    Skeleton implementation of Queryable.

    The default implementation of enumerator() calls the provider's QueryProvider.executeQuery(Queryable) method, but the derived class can override.
